sections.body:
`concurrent` has the following syntax:

```json
{
  "$searchMeta"|"$search": {
    "index": "<index name>", // optional, defaults to "default"
    "<operator>": {
      <operator-specifications>
    },
    "concurrent": true | false,
    ...
  }
}
```

