sections.body:
Consider the following query against the [Sample Mflix Dataset](sample-mflix) collection in the sample data. The query indicates a
concurrent search for movies that contain the term `new york` in the
`title`.

```json
db.movies.aggregate([
  {
    "$search": {
      "text": {
        "path": "title",
        "query": "new york"
      },
      "concurrent": true
    }
  }
])
```
